  schema:name "Dengbej" ;
  schema:description "Kurdish oral storytellers and singers who perform long, unaccompanied vocal narratives — epics, love stories, laments, and histories — drawn from a communal repertoire spanning centuries. The living archive of Kurdish heteroglossia." ;
